<h1 data-nh-numbering="11. ">Architecture:</h1>
<p>
  <strong>Updated November 2025:</strong> Ketchup migrated from AWS Lambda serverless to Docker containers on EC2 (June 2025). This provides 300-400% performance improvement and reduced costs from $450-800/month to ~$150/month.</p>
<h1 data-nh-numbering="12. ">Infrastructure Components:</h1>
<table class="wrapped relative-table" style="width: 100.0%;">
  <colgroup> <col style="width: 20.0%;"/> <col style="width: 40.0%;"/> <col style="width: 40.0%;"/> </colgroup>
  <tbody>
