        </p>
      </th>
      <th>
        <p>
          <strong>Purpose</strong>
        </p>
      </th>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>
        <p>Application Load Balancer</p>
      </td>
      <td>
        <p>ketchup-alb (internet-facing), DNS: ketchup-alb-1659122421.eu-west-1.elb.amazonaws.com, HA across eu-west-1a and eu-west-1b</p>
      </td>
      <td>
        <p>Distribute traffic to both production servers</p>
      </td>
    </tr>
