        <p>prod1: 10.30.0.68 (private), 54.217.126.90 (public), eu-west-1a<br/>prod2: 10.30.165.228 (private), 54.220.15.1 (public), eu-west-1b<br/>OS: Debian-11, CPU: 2 cores/4 vCPU</p>
      </td>
